These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: dannemann, aristoff
Flower: poppy, balloon-flower
1. Flower:poppy is in an even position##4
2. Flower:balloon-flower == Cigar:aristoff##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | dannemann |
| Flower     | balloon-flower    | poppy   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Game: billiard, domino
Music-Genre: country, pop
1. Music-Genre:country is in an odd position##4
2. Game:domino is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Game   | domino | billiard        |
| Music-Genre      | country  | pop |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Sport: sailing, biathlon
Beverage: milk, 7up
1. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
2. Sport:biathlon is on the left of Sport:sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Sport   | biathlon    | sailing |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up |

